name: GrandRapidsAlternateSideParking
0:
”Alexa, ask grand rapids parking what side should I be on”
”Alexa, ask grand rapids parking what side”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: grand rapids parking
des: During winter months on many Grand Rapids, MI streets you can only park on one side of the road. Now you can simply say "Alexa, ask grand rapids parking what side should I be on" and she'll tell you if you need to move the car or not!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
